{"tid":637393,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"念念不忘 必有回響？","createTime":"2018-04-21T17:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T19:11:01.000Z","uid":170864,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6783c64ece86cb445b088fd1b419c662c95fa0f9","tid":637393,"uid":170864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:57:11.000Z","msg":"[借朋友ac]<br />\n同ex分開左2年，一個愛得好深都傷得好深嘅人，其實都心知仲未完全忘記到佢，一直有條刺係個心咁<br />\n<br />\n過左咁長時間，明知自己唔再愛佢，亦無勇氣再面對佢or做返朋友，個天就偏偏鐘意玩人，人亦咁犯賤，前排亦被我發現左佢嘅連登ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> stalk到佢就算分左好耐都記得好多關於我地回憶嘅野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但過左去就係過左去，已經返唔到轉頭。曾經大家都好懦弱，懦弱到錯失左好多野，造成左今日嘅遺憾，或者個遺憾應該唔多唔少都令我地長進，更識捉緊眼前人<br />\n<br />\n我知道你有上連登，唔知你會唔會上感情台睇到呢個post呢. 依家我好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗你祝我幸福 有緣再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a5541080fbde1405aaab1e654c2fd5b684e053","tid":637393,"uid":36402,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:58:38.000Z","msg":"咁都比你搵到佢ac <br />\n整定既"},{"pid":"9fcfea053e7939860a4b89e69856f444cf1e22d6","tid":637393,"uid":161352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T18:44:41.000Z","msg":"句野咁熟"},{"pid":"b7a6b346a572d389493923dbabd91013f5b4483a","tid":637393,"uid":170864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fcfea053e7939860a4b89e69856f444cf1e22d6","tid":637393,"uid":161352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T18:44:41.000Z","msg":"句野咁熟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"葉問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係"},{"pid":"b1a0e1bd29df8238b87aa603a89adc2373da073c","tid":637393,"uid":170864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79a5541080fbde1405aaab1e654c2fd5b684e053","tid":637393,"uid":36402,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:58:38.000Z","msg":"咁都比你搵到佢ac <br